{"tid":1158584,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【班亞弗力正式退役】 傳「吸血仔」羅拔柏迪臣 將成新一任蝙蝠俠","createTime":"2019-05-17T05:30:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-18T16:37:22.000Z","uid":130626,"like":3,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"cad8e409d2312f035c0a5795456b4163c33caa15","tid":1158584,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T05:30:40.000Z","msg":"DC王牌英雄蝙蝠俠獨立作戲即將重製，然而上一任主角班亞弗力（Ben Affleck）已正式退役。而今日就有傳新一任的蝙蝠俠將會是「吸血仔」羅拔柏迪臣（Robert Pattinson）。<br />\n消息人士指， 關於角色羅拔柏迪臣仍在商議階段，一切仍未落實。而其最大對手，就是《變種特攻》（X-Men）的尼古拉斯侯特（Nicholas Hoult），另外型男艾米漢默（Armie Hammer）及艾倫莊遜（ Aaron Taylor-Johnson）亦是候選人之一。新一齣蝙蝠俠獨立作將由《猿人爭霸戰》（Planet of the Apes）導演麥里夫斯（Matt Reeves）執導，並暫定於2021年5月尾上映。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190517/large/1558068237_6890.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190517%2Flarge%2F1558068237_6890.jpg&h=737c81d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190517/large/1558068234_d382.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190517%2Flarge%2F1558068234_d382.jpg&h=43da613b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190517/59610616\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190517%2F59610616&d=2bx9SR3QHfMC8bM4fPAEXyWRWsFhQrZK9M853DAdSZ8%3D&h=c90d9b6b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190517%2F59610616&h=ce6159d8\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190517/59610616</a>"},{"pid":"4b481cb49b9a985e11b429e46b916473bbb6ab39","tid":1158584,"uid":37666,"like":13,"dislike":9,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T02:53:34.000Z","msg":"Ben Affleck型好多囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/